Class FrameSequencer

java.lang.Object
  FrameSequencer

public class FrameSequencer
extends java.lang.Object

Class used to save frames in a movie to a directory and show frames from a movie. This class tracks the directory, base file name, current frame number, and whether this sequence is being shown.
Copyright Georgia Institute of Technology 2005

Author:
Barbara Ericson ericson@cc.gatech.edu
